en:
?? Live the adventure in the middle of nature with an all-terrain electric scooter!

Trott N?ride and Wolftrott propose you to venture in electric scooter on the paths of the country of Caux, along the river Ganzeville and to leave to the meeting of a local producer of cider in Bretteville-du-Grand-Caux which will make you a visit of its exploitation and to taste its cider or its apple juice.

Climb on e-scooters and discover the charms of our nature and our heritage in an atypical way while having fun. A trip in the respect of the environment and without noise pollution for the preservation of the natural elements that you explore.


Conditions of the event :
- Accompanied tour, duration 3h30, forbidden to children under 12 years old.
- Meeting point at 3:45 pm on the parking lot behind the church of Ganzeville.
For a maximum of safety and comfort, you will be initiated during about fifteen minutes.
The guides will adapt to the level of each one, so that you can benefit as well as possible from your stroll.
- Itinerary: paths and small country roads, maximum 25 km/h.
- Good physical condition, suitable clothing, closed shoes, backpack.
- Minimum number of participants: 5, below this number the walk will not take place.

- Numero minimo di partecipanti: 5, al di sotto di questo numero la passeggiata non avr√† luogo.

nl:
?? Beleef een avontuur in de wildernis op een elektrische scooter!

Trott N?ride en Wolftrott stellen u voor om met een elektrische scooter over de paden van het Pays de Caux, langs de rivier de Ganzeville te rijden en in Bretteville-du-Grand-Caux een lokale ciderproducent te ontmoeten die u zijn boerderij laat bezoeken en zijn cider of appelsap laat proeven.
